at|

2@C is always a game force, some don’t play that, but many do. After my 2@D bid ben showed his spades (2@S bid.) As I mentioned before we are in a game force situation. Therefore, 3@S is stronger than 4@S, because it gives us more room to explore.  However, I was close to bidding 4@S, but with my 4 spades and good hearts decided 3 spades was better than 4 spades. Then ben showed slam interest by bidding his diamonds, and I showed further interest by bidding my hearts. |
